19\u201320 coronavirus pandemic by country and territory|Brazil]]\n[[Category:2020 coronavirus pandemic in South America|Brazil]]\n[[Category:2020 in Brazil|coronavirus pandemic]]\n[[Category:Health disasters in Brazil|Coronavirus]]\n", "name_user": "Pravon", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2020_coronavirus_pandemic_in_Brazil"}
